<p>I want to randomly seek a subsequence of length 4 from a larger sequence.</p>  <p>I tried the following code:</p>  <pre><code>import system import random      X = 'ATGCATGCTAGCTAGTAAACGTACGTACGTACGATGCTAATATAGAGGGGCTTCGTACCCCTGA'     Y = [random.choice(X) for i in range(4)]     print(Y) </code></pre>  <p>But it selects 4 distinct elements from X and not a sequence of length 4 in continuity.</p>